<!--pages/zizhanghaobangdiingzhanghao/index.wxml-->
<form bindsubmit='authbind'>
<view class="container">
  <view class='contianer-info'>请在此填写您收到的授权码</view>

  <view class='contianer-input'>
    <view class='contianer-input-label'>授权码</view>
    <view class='contianer-input-wrop'><input type='number'  maxlength='6' placeholder='请输入收到的6位数字授权码' name="code"></input></view>
  </view>
  <view class='contianer-info'>注：当授权人在“共享我的资金帐号”界面输入您的手机号，您通过短信获取到授权码后，可在此界面输入授权码，将授权人的帐号绑定在您的帐号下。</view>
  <button form-type='submit' class='contianer-button'>确认绑定</button>
</view>
</form>
